videos.headline: Azubuike powers into the end zone
videos.description: Isaiah Azubuike uses blazing speed to get into the red zone then powers his way into the end zone to put Arkansas State up 14-7.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Azubuike powers into the end zone) 2020/09/05 ESHEET

videos.headline: Clark follows blocks to paydirt
videos.description: Rodrigues Clark follows behind his lead blocker and makes a move to cap off a 14-yard touchdown run.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Clark follows blocks to paydirt) 2020/09/05 ESHEET

videos.headline: White finds Dykes wide open for 6
videos.description: Brady White finds a wide-open Sean Dykes in the back of the end zone for a Tigers touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (White finds Dykes wide open for 6) 2020/09/05 ESHEET

videos.headline: Memphis fake punts to the big man
videos.description: With a 17-point lead, the Memphis Tigers run a punt fake to defensive tackle Joseph Dorceus for a 25-yard gain.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Memphis fake punts to the big man) 2020/09/05 ESHEET
